@startuml activity-trusted-contact
!theme plain
title Activity — Trusted Contact emergency

|#LightYellow|Phase A: Patient đăng ký TC|
start
:Patient mở TrustedContactsScreen;
:Bấm "Thêm người thân tin cậy";
:Paste ví TC + label (vd "Mẹ");

if (Ví hợp lệ + khác patient?) then (NO)
  :Highlight error;
  stop
else (YES)
endif

:Biometric MFA;
:Sign TrustedContactPermit(active=true);
:POST /api/relayer/trusted-contact;
:Contract setTrustedContactBySig:\nisTrustedContact[P][TC] = true\n+ emit TrustedContactSet;

if (TC đã activate encryption key?) then (NO)
  :Error "TC chưa đăng nhập app";
  stop
else (YES)
endif

:runEncryptionCeremony(TC);
:For each current record:\n  encrypt (cid, aesKey)\n  cho TC's NaCl pubkey;
:POST /api/key-share/bulk-trusted-contact;
:Backend lưu KeyShare rows\nsource='trusted-contact';

|#LightGray|Phase A+: Auto pre-share record mới (background)|
:Patient tạo record mới (Activity 14);
:autoPreShareNewRecord:\nfor each TC active\n  encrypt + bulk pre-share;
note right
  TC luôn có KeyShare cho
  mọi record mới, kể cả TC offline
end note

|#LightBlue|Phase B: TC truy cập emergency|
:TC login app;
:Mở record của patient;
:GET /api/key-share/record/:cidHash;
:Backend gate canAccess(P, TC, cid);
:Contract check isTrustedContact\n(Footgun #2 fix);

if (TC active?) then (YES)
  :Trả encryptedPayload;
  :TC mobile decrypt NaCl box\n→ (cid, aesKey);
  :Fetch IPFS + decrypt AES-GCM;
  :Render record;
else (NO)
  :403 Forbidden;
endif

|#LightCoral|Phase C: Patient revoke TC|
:Patient chọn TC → thu hồi;
:Sign TrustedContactPermit(false);
:POST /api/relayer/trusted-contact;
:Contract: isTrustedContact[P][TC] = false\n+ emit TrustedContactRevoked;
:Backend handleTrustedContactRevoked:\n- mark status='revoked'\n- cascade revoke KeyShare rows\n  source='trusted-contact';

:TC mở record sau revoke;
:canAccess → false → 403;

note right
  ⚠ Limitation: TC vẫn có thể
  decrypt OFFLINE nếu local cache
  còn — envelope encryption không
  thể un-share data đã ra ngoài
end note

stop

@enduml
